00:39:40,140 --> 00:39:40,980
Taman Guanlan.

515
00:39:44,620 --> 00:39:45,700
Pikirkanlah lagi.

516
00:39:47,580 --> 00:39:50,980
Aku tidak perlu berpikir.
Gaya hidupku sangat teratur.

517
00:39:51,380 --> 00:39:53,860
Aku bekerja di puskesmas Dongyuan
